parameters.townshipsMouseover:
Township Data
These layers display administrative areas are used to organize land surveying and natural resource exploration.
parameters.miningMouseover:
Mining Data
These map layers contain mining such as current claims and abandoned mine sites.
parameters.forestryMouseover:
Forestry Data
These map layers show forestry related information.
parameters.communityMouseover:
Community Data
These map layers contain information provided by the community about Culture, Environment, Habitat, Subsistence and Transportation.
parameters.boundaryMouseover:
Boundary Data
These map layers display boundaries information.
parameters.crowdsourceMouseover:
Community Crowdsourced Data
These map layers contain content contributed by community members.
parameters.projectMouseover:
Project Data
These map layers display spatial documents related to the current project.
parameters.otherMouseover:
Other Data
These map layers display additional useful features.
